com.avaya.csta.binding

Class GetLinkStatusResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.ecma.csta.CastorObject
      • com.avaya.csta.binding.GetLinkStatusResponse
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class GetLinkStatusResponse
extends ch.ecma.csta.CastorObject
implements java.io.Serializable
    Response to GetLinkStatus request that contains the status of the requested link(s). The response has these parameters:

    GetLinkStatusResponse Parameters
    linkList Always provided a list of LinkStatus structures of either all links or the requested link. The LinkStatus structure is described below.
    linkListCount Always provided Number of LinkStatus structures in linkList. Currently, this value is always 1.
